         <div>
            <head>5.8.1885 Mittwoch</head>
            <p>
               <placeName type="write" key="49289">Rigi Kaltbad</placeName> August 5 1885 Wednesday.</p>
            <p>Walked or rather tried to walk up the <placeName key="49373">Rigi
               Rothstock</placeName> with <persName key="7851">Schwabach</persName>
               <note type="reg">Paul</note>. I tried to take a short cut, which are proverbially the longest.
               Soon we got to a place when we could neither get up nor down, so we had to go back.
                  Schwabachs<note type="reg">
                  <persName key="18297">Leonie</persName>, <persName key="18296">Julius</persName> und <persName key="7851">Paul</persName>
               </note> travelled away at 1.45. In the afternoon I took a long walk with <persName key="1863">Valentin</persName>. First to <placeName key="49374">Unterstetten</placeName> from there to the Klösterli and then back home. He of
               course told me all about his ailments etc. and how the eating in Spain made him sick.
               Came home about 7 and dined at Table d&#x2019;Hôte.</p>
         </div>
